## HK module

### General - HK 
* This module allows to create a client-to-customer billing agreement in one server call
* This module can only be used by the pay protocol
* You can make a standard transaction and also open a billing agreement
* Agreement data can not be updated by these api only by manual actions in the transaction management system. If there is such a demand, you should contact Token.

### Stage 1 - relevent parameters for Pay protocol
```html
<input type="hidden" name="HK" value="True">
<input type="hidden" name="Tash" value="24">
<input type="hidden" name="OnlyOnApprove" value="True">
<input type="hidden" name="FirstDate" value="yyyy-mm-dd">
<input type="hidden" name="freq" value="1">
```
#### Passed parameters
|Parameter name | Description | Value format | Required | General |
|---------------|-------------|--------------|----------|---------|
| HK | Pay Page in HK mode | True / False <br> defualt set to False | Optional | Additional info in HK article  |
| freq | payment frequency | Number in months| Optional | 
| FirstDate | First payment date | YYY-MM-DD | Optional |  |
| Tash | Number of payments | Number of payments | Required | For HK without limit insert 999 |
| OnlyOnApprove | only if the first payment is approved the deal is closed | True / False <br> defualt set to False | Optional |  |


<!--
### Example payment page in direct debit billing mode

* The system will add the word "monthly"
* The system will show the customer the number of direct debit charges
* If the charges are unlimited (999), the system will not show the customer the number of charges


<img src="https://imgur.com/y2OhvyF.png" alt="HK Payment Page Example" width="400" height="200">


The image above shows how the customer will see the charges.

-->

### HK Returned Parameters:
In addition to the standard parameters of the pay protocol
An additional parameter named hkid = agreement number will be added

For Exmaple:
```http
https://pay.hyp.co.il/result?HKId=64238&Id=5334206&CCode=0&Amount=100&ACode=0012345&Order=12345678910&Fild1=Michael%20Isarel&Fild2=&Fild3=&Sign=8a30b17a53e7f6fe5c7f8268db1638ee010eae83bead8fa0ec1a9760407a3ac9&Bank=6&Payments=24&UserId=203269535&Brand=2&Issuer=2&L4digit=0000&street=levanon%203&city=netanya&zip=42361&cell=0506400013&Coin=1&Tmonth=3&Tyear=2019&Hesh=EZ
```

#### An example of an agreement in the management system

<img src="https://pay.hyp.co.il/yaadpay/images/apiary/HK%20Menu.png">

#### In the managment system you can:
1. Update Amount and date of charge
<img src="https://yaadpay.yaad.net/developers/assets/ScreenShot2017-07-23at17.03.32.png">
2. Stop/ Start charge
<img src="https://yaadpay.yaad.net/developers/assets/ScreenShot2017-07-23at17.04.22.png">
3. Update credit card information
<img src="https://yaadpay.yaad.net/developers/assets/ScreenShot2017-07-23at17.03.37.png">
4. update Update invoice details
<img src="https://yaadpay.yaad.net/developers/assets/ScreenShot2017-07-23at17.04.15.png">

<b>In addition, it is possible to update a sweeping amount for all agreements by uploading an Excel file!</b>

### Make a transaction and creating HK in one call
|Parameter name | Description | Value format | Required | General |
|---------------|-------------|--------------|----------|---------|
| Amount | Monthly amount for charge | Number | Optional |
| HK | Pay Page in HK mode | True / False <br> defualt set to False | Optional | Additional info in HK article  |
| freq | payment frequency | Number in months| Optional | 
| Tash | Number of payments | Number of payments <br> unlimited = 999 | Required | For HK without limit insert 999 |
| OnlyOnApprove | only if the first payment is approved the deal is closed | True / False <br> defualt set to False | Optional |  |
| FirstDate | First payment date | YYY-MM-DD | Optional |  |
| TashFirstPayment| The amount of a single transaction | Numbers only | Optional |
| FirstPaymentTash | The number of charges for the single transaction | Numbers only | Optional |

#### Example of html request
```html
<form action="https://pay.hyp.co.il/p/" method="post" target="_blank" accept-charset="UTF-8"
enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded" autocomplete="off" novalidate>

<input type="hidden" name="action" value="pay">
<input type="hidden" name="PassP" value="1234">
<input type="hidden" name="SendHesh" value="True">
<input type="hidden" name="HK" value="True">
<input type="hidden" name="OnlyOnApprove" value="True">
<input type="hidden" name="TashFirstPayment" value="50">
<input type="hidden" name="FixTash" value="True">
<input type="hidden" name="FirstPaymentTash" value="3">
<input type="hidden" name="Info" value="">

<input type="hidden" name="Amount" value="120">

<input type="hidden" name="sendemail" value="True">
<input type="hidden" name="UTF8" value="True">
<input type="hidden" name="UTF8out" value="True">
<input type="hidden" name="UTF8out" value="True">
<input type="hidden" name="MoreData" value="True">
<input type="hidden" name="Coin" value="1">
<input type="hidden" name="Tash" value="999">
<input type="hidden" name="Masof" value="0010020610">

<input type="hidden" name="FirstDate" value="yyyy-mm-dd">
<!-- לשים לב לפומרט של התאריך -->



<input type="submit" value="שלח">
</form>
```

#### Example of payment page in this status
<img src="https://yaadpay.yaad.net/developers/assets/ScreenShot2017-07-23at17.15.15.png">

### Termination / Activation of Agreement by api: (Change Status of Direct Debit Agreement)
#### HTTP request example
```http
POST /p/ HTTP/1.1
Host: pay.hyp.co.il
Content-Length: 362
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

action=HKStatus&Masof=0010020610&HKId=64239&NewStat=1
```

#### Passed parameters
| Field Name  | Description  | Value format |
|----------------|--------------|-----|
| action | Description of the request | HKSatus|
| Masof | Masof number in Hypay servers | Numbers only |
| HKId | Agreement number | Numbers only |
| NewStat | Termination = 1 <br> Activation = 2 |
| PassP | Authentication with password, Required if this your chosen authentication method |

#### The response retunes in the format
HKId=xxxx&CCode=0

If CCode is 0 , the request was approved succesfuly, else it's an error

<b>Common errors</b>
| CCode | Information |
|-------|------|
| 905 | Wrong Parameter value |
| 906 | Agreement dosn't exists |
